EN: Their company has many experts to guide employees.

ZH: 内行人总能够找到解决问题的最佳方法。
EN: Experts can always find the best way to solve problems.

ZH: 要成为内行，需要持续不断地学习和积累经验。
EN: To become an expert, you need to continuously learn and accumulate experience.

ZH: 他是这个行业的内行，被誉为权威。
EN: He is an expert in this industry and is acclaimed as an authority.
